[[File:Taraloon_Pirate_Complex.jpg|thumb|right|250px|The Taraloon Pirate Complex]]
The '''Taraloon Pirate Complex''' was an underground base build on the uncharted [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Taraloon]] by the [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] [[Drek Drednar]] and his crew. It was equipped with perimeter [[Sensor/Legends|sensors]], maintenance bays, [[Hangar/Legends|hangars]] for the ship ''[[Sable III]]'' and the [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] under Drednar's command, medical facilities, dining rooms, recreation centers and comfortable quarters. There was also a large cache where the pirate loot was stored.<ref name="SD">{{JournalCite|5|Stand and Deliver}}</ref>

